{"tid":308863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年青人, 想置業應耐心等待泡沫爆破後樓價大跌才入市！","createTime":"2017-07-04T14:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T12:24:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3547e63bed3795e29db020f04145e1b7ab9d17d6","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"致香港的年青人：<br />\n<br />\n妳願意用二十至三十年的青春去換一層樓嗎？做一生樓奴值得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n於香港買樓等於交重稅，In Form 4 Economics, it says &quot;in Hong Kong, land is a tax&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n香港稅基狹窄，財政支出靠賣地收入，所以香港買樓等於交重稅。加上發展商奸狡掠水食水深，官商勾結利益輸送，買樓等於交重稅兼幫地產商打一生工，所以現在應該先關注自己的事業，儲夠金錢，等待最適當時機才入市買樓！<br />\n<br />\n但 不要期望政府會幫忙，特區政府與地產商之間，擺明官商勾結利益輸送(天匯事件不了了之，梁展文事件等等)，點會干預市場壓低樓價幫市民置業。想政府幫市民 置業，除非特區政府被推翻，成立新的民主香港政府啦！特區政府只會將現時買不到樓的八十後青年標籤為&quot;低能兒童&quot;，卻不會出手相助！<br />\n<br />\n現時樓價瘋癲，脫離實際經濟因素，現在買樓等於用二十至三十年的青春去換一層負資產的樓。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但不要緊，從來都是物極必反。泡沫吹得愈大，爆破後跌得愈勁！貪婪的地產商加上腐敗無能的特區政府，會促使呢個泡沫愈吹愈大，直至失控爆破。</span>學梁錦松講，樓市有咁耐風流,，有咁耐折墮。年輕人應耐心等待泡沫爆破後樓價大跌(eg沙士價)才人入市！"},{"pid":"ffb83eb64d60769741361fddc40b99dd0fc9fec2","tid":308863,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29cd4da476b596b27259a160bcf8e49a88eecc17","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"作者補充：<br />\n<br />\n1)怎樣脫離樓奴困境？<br />\n<br />\n2003年沙士時的樓價大概是1997年樓市高峰期的三成，即妳所儲的三成首期己足夠妳付清所有樓價，不需向銀行借貸供樓，即妳不需做樓奴。<br />\n<br />\n2)樓市有機會跌7成嗎？<br />\n<br />\n絕 對有機會跌7成，甚至有機會跌9成。只要泡沫吹得愈大，爆破後跌得愈勁！1997年樓市高峰期時那有人會想到之後樓價會跌7-8成，當時的人只相信樓市會 升多幾十年，沙士只是觸發樓市終極一跌，就算沒有沙士當時樓市亦會跌6-7成。1989年日本樓市高峰期時那有人會想到之後樓市會跌足20年，現在的日本 樓市仍在谷底難以反彈，因1989年日本樓市需要供三代，應驗了泡沫吹得愈大，爆破後跌得愈勁！<br />\n<br />\n3)年青人，妳們最大的本錢是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n應該 是青春吧！有青春便可充分運用&quot;耐性資本&quot;，股神巴菲特所說的&quot;耐性資本&quot;是指成功的投資者必須具備雙重的耐心，能以無比的耐性等候入市的機會，入市以後 要有同樣的耐心等候股價上升來反映其內在價值，体現價值技投資的精髓，別人貪婪我恐懼(1997年時)，別人恐懼時我貪婪(2003年時)。正如德國股神 科思托蘭尼所講：&quot;賺錢就是那麼容易，跟群眾對著幹！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n4)對於年青人來講，供樓的最大成本是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n供樓的成本不單是利息，對於年青人來講，富爸爸說供樓的最大成本可能是&quot;放棄學習創業和投資的機會&quot;。因創業和投資確實需要交學費(即輸錢)，買樓付首期已減少了創業和投資的資本，加上負債後的心理壓力，確實令不少人對創業和投資卻步。<br />\n<br />\n5)泡沫真的會爆破嗎？<br />\n<br />\n百 分之一百會，從17世紀荷蘭的鬱金香泡沫、1720年南海泡沫、1928年美國股市投機泡沫、1990年代日本股市樓市泡沫、1997年香港股市樓市泡 沫、2000年科網股泡沫等等，最終都以爆破結束！偉大的科學家牛頓都在泡沫爆破後輸光身家，並說：&quot;我能計算出天體的運行軌跡，卻無法計算群眾的瘋 狂！&quot;"},{"pid":"235dbc6e004c50d21856003a317a61ea6b94ab2b","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fd3e6414b3e38d00eedae7bb9b5e9d0e402677","tid":308863,"uid":93083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:23:51.000Z","msg":"爆過兩次之後，所有香港人都知跌樓價係大好時機=永遠唔會再跌"},{"pid":"09f6526227b9877cbb8a4423d12bf866df85b805","tid":308863,"uid":30484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"爆完又繼續等升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294f542aa59d9a56974ae33ab3613408b5a0c7a0","tid":308863,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"等淡友絕跡"},{"pid":"8fe117ca226eb710266ff507ef9819fa80ff1d35","tid":308863,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"係呀跌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4045f2b135721a40db999ee740a39354977d43c","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆過兩次之後，所有香港人都知跌樓價係大好時機=永遠唔會再跌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/001545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F001545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3568a580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a19abec60a10552b293b9b49b53d8cab2575615","tid":308863,"uid":71133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"本身其實好難大跌，但越來越多廢中廢老開始貪心瘋狂入市就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952df43245d671674e721048f6dd6515bf87b50a","tid":308863,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦，到時班濕鳩業主打死都唔放，變哂做租盤，等到個價升番上去先賣，你班廢青以為咁就買到樓呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defafe3f76cc8ad1db68eb8817d4c3567914f88a","tid":308863,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"只會升不會跌丫，租一世樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0892dff4a8a06ac22ae0637faea30da7437c47b4","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8612bed135a6ed1341a5d4e6963622d2c044845f","tid":308863,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"留名等睇有人入黎屌淡友"},{"pid":"460db0c387bfd73fc5b7485f95f7ccefb745548b","tid":308863,"uid":36567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只會升不會跌丫，租一世樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2047前夕會跌 未來20年不會跌"},{"pid":"a887adf9f3b867680e8dd3b46f7de4900f6f168d","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de0b29562ca7a184011dae5e44acefac0387e08","tid":308863,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"冇可能會跌"},{"pid":"6e098f80c0ee4eb4a2ac54332ed9a515d25ae474","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇可能會跌</blockquote><br />\n絕對會跌"},{"pid":"a8ed1602907b4821f6d2e65453284b993fa3658d","tid":308863,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"On9到依家仲信會爆，吹左咁多年算罷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有最高只有更高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb6a906336ee588bbdcaa5c08d0529c2463d64f","tid":308863,"uid":120719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"唔撚好傻啦。<br />\n大把人有現金係手，大漲小回。<br />\n一跌10%大把人入手。<br />\n成日有人同以前去做比較，真係好on9.<br />\n97香港人口有幾多，現在有幾多？<br />\n97買樓比幾多成首期，現在比幾多？<br />\n成日同日本比較，日本有冇中國照呀？<br />\n中國對香港態度係唔會比你起佢飛腳，但又唔會比你死。<br />\n<br />\n講句真心，成日話買唔樓既人。根本心目中係冇價的，個市係幾多錢佢都買唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2fd2fee142b5499430745aae877b5dc6d8e55d","tid":308863,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41ce2b8dcc20a57728d76cbf0b9dc01bbc409d6","tid":308863,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚好傻啦。<br />\n大把人有現金係手，大漲小回。<br />\n一跌10%大把人入手。<br />\n成日有人同以前去做比較，真係好on9.<br />\n97香港人口有幾多，現在有幾多？<br />\n97買樓比幾多成首期，現在比幾多？<br />\n成日同日本比較，日本有冇中國照呀？<br />\n中國對香港態度係唔會比你起佢飛腳，但又唔會比你死。<br />\n<br />\n講句真心，成日話買唔樓既人。根本心目中係冇價的，個市係幾多錢佢都買唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇升而家就買啦，仲等跌10%,  已有三層樓，等緊買第四層，一夠錢就買，升跌都唔放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9926ae5eef34c5185cf16724184d84a267551fb","tid":308863,"uid":120719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔撚好傻啦。<br />\n大把人有現金係手，大漲小回。<br />\n一跌10%大把人入手。<br />\n成日有人同以前去做比較，真係好on9.<br />\n97香港人口有幾多，現在有幾多？<br />\n97買樓比幾多成首期，現在比幾多？<br />\n成日同日本比較，日本有冇中國照呀？<br />\n中國對香港態度係唔會比你起佢飛腳，但又唔會比你死。<br />\n<br />\n講句真心，成日話買唔樓既人。根本心目中係冇價的，個市係幾多錢佢都買唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇升而家就買啦，仲等跌10%,  已有三層樓，等緊買第四層，一夠錢就買，升跌都唔放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢期抄股好，個市旺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ec9753fb3d815afdee6806bc2f3da5b0061c31","tid":308863,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"打左十年飛機都仲打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係爆就快，跌3成都all in入市"},{"pid":"239a9314a198ff57135176229af7c59fa508af3c","tid":308863,"uid":22893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚好傻啦。<br />\n大把人有現金係手，大漲小回。<br />\n一跌10%大把人入手。<br />\n成日有人同以前去做比較，真係好on9.<br />\n97香港人口有幾多，現在有幾多？<br />\n97買樓比幾多成首期，現在比幾多？<br />\n成日同日本比較，日本有冇中國照呀？<br />\n中國對香港態度係唔會比你起佢飛腳，但又唔會比你死。<br />\n<br />\n講句真心，成日話買唔樓既人。根本心目中係冇價的，個市係幾多錢佢都買唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n現揸兩層，8年前個個叫我唔好買會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四百幾萬樓我按五成，4年後有資金空間轉窿拎多一球出黎諗住買多間，舊樓租俾人又係叫我唔好買會跌，我按七成照供，舊樓照租俾人萬九蚊，我住新買個到，而家一層當年四百幾而家七百萬，一層6百萬入而家750萬，而家每月供萬七蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年叫我唔好買啲朋友而家仲同緊老母住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}